<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://femminismorivoluzionario.blogspot.com/2023/02/con-questi-carichi-di-lavoro-da-fare-in.html'>Con questi carichi di lavoro da fare in pochissime ore non ce la facciamo più, e il salario non basta neanche per sopravvivere!</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-786538004729528580' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<div style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: #080808; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 16px; padding: 3px 6px;">Avviato lo stato di agitazione, verso lo sciopero delle lavoratrici di pulizie e ausiliariato degli asili comunali.&nbsp;</div><div style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: #080808; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 16px; padding: 3px 6px;">Rappresentanti delle lavoratrici ne parleranno nell'<b>Assemblea proletaria anticapitalista nazionale a Roma del 18 febbraio </b>e</div><div style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: #080808; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 16px; padding: 3px 6px;">nell'<b>assemblea Donne/Lavoratrici telematica del 23 febbraio ore 17</b> (seguira' link).</div><div style="background: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: #080808; font-family: Verdana; font-size: 16px; padding: 3px 6px;"><br /></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5X7gLTK2hRotTxMBMEYRx_vJeQ4eHz2XRcq07ph7a75IVCvdN2_dBqZeWE-Awv8t7peHnnQX9C8SB1YeY7q3wDjWv42cZNLYKBQMLHQTR2cihdl4am1L6Iq491KF79sl7n-nadM7vYgdgjyzPD4H-TBUR-cQz9IIfjzGNukAPyYbQCERowxRhvKgA/s1589/SERVIZI%20INTEGRATI%20SRL%20-%20Proclamazione%20stato%20di%20agitazione%20e%20richiesta%20di%20conciliazione%20preventiva%20obbligatoria_page-0001.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="1589" data-original-width="1068" height="640" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh5X7gLTK2hRotTxMBMEYRx_vJeQ4eHz2XRcq07ph7a75IVCvdN2_dBqZeWE-Awv8t7peHnnQX9C8SB1YeY7q3wDjWv42cZNLYKBQMLHQTR2cihdl4am1L6Iq491KF79sl7n-nadM7vYgdgjyzPD4H-TBUR-cQz9IIfjzGNukAPyYbQCERowxRhvKgA/w430-h640/SERVIZI%20INTEGRATI%20SRL%20-%20Proclamazione%20stato%20di%20agitazione%20e%20richiesta%20di%20conciliazione%20preventiva%20obbligatoria_page-0001.jpg" width="430" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhKDkg7rt5HKGfzQmthhNV1z-ppxJ_zF6A_-ExQCHEseD71PVUDhKjS7SlB7U_UR9W28oQgUo2ToFlNAEC5cFK6MeHHqW6hLkO2NGVR7S3a1e4JBJpRd5tXjQYNibOSyqser68qn7o8VzSx9ikgXS6MCd3QFRzhZlLjU2HW0xBqbM46t4sQIUoWxUKD/s1087/SERVIZI%20INTEGRATI%20SRL%20-%20Proclamazione%20stato%20di%20agitazione%20e%20richiesta%20di%20conciliazione%20preventiva%20obbligatoria_page-0002.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="821" data-original-width="1087" height="303" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhKDkg7rt5HKGfzQmthhNV1z-ppxJ_zF6A_-ExQCHEseD71PVUDhKjS7SlB7U_UR9W28oQgUo2ToFlNAEC5cFK6MeHHqW6hLkO2NGVR7S3a1e4JBJpRd5tXjQYNibOSyqser68qn7o8VzSx9ikgXS6MCd3QFRzhZlLjU2HW0xBqbM46t4sQIUoWxUKD/w400-h303/SERVIZI%20INTEGRATI%20SRL%20-%20Proclamazione%20stato%20di%20agitazione%20e%20richiesta%20di%20conciliazione%20preventiva%20obbligatoria_page-0002.jpg" width="400" /></a></div>
