<meta content='https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhql7dSG6Ew-xfgaWib5FkHsfXTgZ8eBWsy8deLWNOiNM9NHyEdF2dHPn15v21vSzORnFM0y-adqu8wVFTv9mBnppfzfTuqfvdIivd5rPvAzNYYqs66VMEpzBl0uSKR-7midlrYCViGtg3Xtvszv0Sr2gpBQ6a9W-FzcG4DniGr4yKITffL-MlsGfLY/w640-h480/1.jpg' itemprop='image_url'/>
<meta content='4067284372754125534' itemprop='blogId'/>
<meta content='4104884209168199555' itemprop='postId'/>
<a name='4104884209168199555'></a>
<h3 class='post-title entry-title' itemprop='name'>
<a href='https://femminismorivoluzionario.blogspot.com/2023/02/a-fianco-delle-nostre-sorelle-turche.html'>A fianco delle nostre sorelle turche, onore alle martiri del regime di Erdogan e dell'imperialismo</a>
</h3>
<div class='post-header'>
<div class='post-header-line-1'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-body entry-content' id='post-body-4104884209168199555' itemprop='description articleBody'>
<b><span style="font-size: large;">L'Unione delle donne comuniste commemora i martiri del partito e della rivoluzione.</span></b><div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhql7dSG6Ew-xfgaWib5FkHsfXTgZ8eBWsy8deLWNOiNM9NHyEdF2dHPn15v21vSzORnFM0y-adqu8wVFTv9mBnppfzfTuqfvdIivd5rPvAzNYYqs66VMEpzBl0uSKR-7midlrYCViGtg3Xtvszv0Sr2gpBQ6a9W-FzcG4DniGr4yKITffL-MlsGfLY/s4160/1.jpg" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="3120" data-original-width="4160" height="480" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEhql7dSG6Ew-xfgaWib5FkHsfXTgZ8eBWsy8deLWNOiNM9NHyEdF2dHPn15v21vSzORnFM0y-adqu8wVFTv9mBnppfzfTuqfvdIivd5rPvAzNYYqs66VMEpzBl0uSKR-7midlrYCViGtg3Xtvszv0Sr2gpBQ6a9W-FzcG4DniGr4yKITffL-MlsGfLY/w640-h480/1.jpg" width="640" /></a></div><br /><div class="separator" style="clear: both; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;"><a href="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgo9rraW2Zn6rCnx1MwJTbDdNs2ZgWjitCL6t_rxDC8vxEsXFaxkv5Oi1VO8bdp9AjHlv9R1RzH3o5zmtEw12EL3pGSncu1PJiUo4u45tNik9evaelincFNNlBm9mLoqeEHDidnPoAH6WPT3Jh2rMJJowffDVDVsccoAaEjJoqOK1c8sQzlx61WELtW/s1160/2.png" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="870" data-original-width="1160" height="480" src="https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgo9rraW2Zn6rCnx1MwJTbDdNs2ZgWjitCL6t_rxDC8vxEsXFaxkv5Oi1VO8bdp9AjHlv9R1RzH3o5zmtEw12EL3pGSncu1PJiUo4u45tNik9evaelincFNNlBm9mLoqeEHDidnPoAH6WPT3Jh2rMJJowffDVDVsccoAaEjJoqOK1c8sQzlx61WELtW/w640-h480/2.png" width="640" /></a></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: justify;"><i><br /></i></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: justify;"><i>Stralci dal loro comunicato:</i><br /><b>"Non esiteremo a seguire le loro orme!"</b></div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; font-weight: bold; text-align: justify;">L'evento di commemorazione è stato organizzato il 2 febbraio, data del martirio dei compagni Eylem, Emel, Özlem, Dilek e Sevda, nella guerriglia di 12 anni fa.</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; font-weight: bold; text-align: justify;">Hanno partecipato le donne combattenti della Brigata Martire Nubar Ozanyan.</div><div class="separator" style="clear: both; font-weight: bold; text-align: justify;">Queste compagne "Erano le avanguardie della lotta per la libertà delle donne e delle persone LGBTI. La loro esistenza e lotta erano una guerra per raggiungere il successo. Per questo, dobbiamo imparare dalle loro lotte e vite. Continueremo la nostra marcia sulle loro orme senza esitazione."</div></div></div>
<div style='clear: both;'></div>
</div>
<div class='post-footer'>
<div class='post-footer-line post-footer-line-1'><span class='post-author vcard'>
